Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.30,0:21:31.85,ED-zh,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4\3a33}我们嬉闹着笑作一团
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.39,0:21:37.85,ED-zh,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4\3a33}虽说这画面再平常不过
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.77,0:21:40.40,ED-zh,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4\3a33}但我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.40,0:21:43.99,ED-zh,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4\3a33\3c&HEB980D&}昔日不能重现
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.99,0:21:47.20,ED-zh,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4\3a33\3c&HEB980D&}往事不会再来
